narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned much about how electromagnetic signals propagate through both 1-dimensional and 3-dimensional situations, how to use circuits to model and control this propagation, and how to think about waves in the complex domain.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think the beginning is too slow. The first 4-5 weeks (basically a review of intro E&M) should be condensed into 2 weeks, and more time should be spend on expanding the super interesting last part of the course (radio waves & antennas).
